{"title":"Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #7: Scott Addict RC","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-scott-addict-rc","date":1741175891000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-scott-addict-rc\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #7: Scott Addict RC</a></p>\n\n<p>Whether you’re in the market for a new bike or just want to try out some of the world’s very best, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">Cyclist Track Days</a> offer a unique experience to test the latest top-end bikes from the leading brands on the market. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next up in our run-through of some of the incredible bikes that you can test ride at this years Track Days is the Scott Addict RC.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Released in 2024 to much hype because of its claimed 5.9kg total bike weight, the Scott Addict RC will be ridden by <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/tom-pidcock-profile\">Tom Pidcock</a> and the Q36.5 Pro Cycling team this year.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Cyclist</em> deputy editor James Spender recently reviewed the new Scott Addict RC and said it was the best Addict so far (more on the bike’s history <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/scott-addict-history\">here</a>).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>James tested the build with a SRAM Red AXS groupset and Syncros Capital SL wheels, which came out to a total weight of 5.87kg in a size medium. The build that Scott is bringing to Cycling Track Days this year is the Scott Addict RC 10, which comes with a Shimano Ultegra Di2 groupset and Syncros Capital 1.0s wheels. That spec retails for £6,599 and is said to weigh 7.1kg.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can read James’s full review <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/scott-addict-rc-road-bike-2025-review\">here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Scott Addict RC will be at the following Track Days events:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>26<sup>th</sup> April 2025, Odd Down Cycle Track Bath,<br />17<sup>th</sup> May 2025, Lee Valley VeloPark London,<br />7<sup>th</sup> June 2025, The Brownlee Centre, Leeds</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information on Cyclist Track Days click <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/cc/cyclist-track-days-2025-3855053\" target=\"_blank\">BOOK YOUR TICKET HERE</a></strong></h3>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-trek-madone-slr\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #5: Trek Madone SLR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-van-rysel-rcr\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #1: Van Rysel RCR</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/scott-addict-rc-road-bike-2025-review\">Scott Addict RC road bike review</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 info and how to get tickets</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n    